                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='Starting July 2024, order volume more than doubled but average order value dropped from around $7,700 to $3,200. The business appears to have shifted from high value B2B orders toward a higher volume retail model.' captured-sheet='Avg Order Value Trend' id='2' />
                  <story-point caption='Bikes account for 77% of all revenue at $94.7M. Road Bikes and Mountain Bikes alone make up over 85% of that figure. Accessories and Clothing generate high order counts but contribute very little to overall revenue.' captured-sheet='Product &amp; Customer Analysis' id='3' />
                  <story-point caption='North America drives 72% of total revenue. The Southwest territory leads all regions at $27.1M. Canada and Northwest follow closely. European markets are comparable in size but significantly smaller than North America.' captured-sheet='Geographic Map' id='4'>
                    <capturedDeltas>
